import React from "react";
import { Dropdown, Menu } from "semantic-ui-react";

const HomeHeader = () => (
    <Menu>
        <Menu.Item>Home</Menu.Item>
        <Dropdown text="Shopping" pointing className="link item">
            <Dropdown.Menu>
                <Dropdown.Header>Categories</Dropdown.Header>
                <Dropdown.Item>
                    <Dropdown text="Clothing">
                        <Dropdown.Menu>
                            <Dropdown.Header>Proj1</Dropdown.Header>
                            <Dropdown.Item>Proj2</Dropdown.Item>
                            <Dropdown.Item>Proj3</Dropdown.Item>
                            <Dropdown.Item>Proj4</Dropdown.Item>
                            <Dropdown.Item>Proj5</Dropdown.Item>
                            <Dropdown.Divider />
                            <Dropdown.Header>Womens</Dropdown.Header>
                        </Dropdown.Menu>
                    </Dropdown>
                </Dropdown.Item>
                <Dropdown.Item>Home Goods</Dropdown.Item>
                <Dropdown.Item>Bedroom</Dropdown.Item>
                <Dropdown.Divider />
                <Dropdown.Header>Order</Dropdown.Header>
                <Dropdown.Item>Status</Dropdown.Item>
                <Dropdown.Item>Cancellations</Dropdown.Item>
            </Dropdown.Menu>
        </Dropdown>
        <Menu.Item>Forums</Menu.Item>
        <Menu.Item>Contact Us</Menu.Item>
    </Menu>
);

export default HomeHeader;
